{"tid":1367073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解唔見有人封殺呢間旅行社","createTime":"2019-07-26T06:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:32:55.000Z","uid":92680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"836c8582996e5ae6ffcb7672e12096cefeb11dce","tid":1367073,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"就係大航假期呢間係tvb落廣告嘅旅行社呀<br />\n此旅行社於tvb落廣告，亦有於big big shop出優惠，姐係間接幫助tvb。<br />\n雖然我相信各位巴絲未必會報團，但希望可以提下你地身邊嘅長輩。<br />\n因為呢間旅行社係宣傳單張印錯會叫員工直接塗走字樣，然後當無事，本人已取一本被塗後亦可清楚睇見未塗前字樣的單張。<br />\n從此3張圖可見<br />\n<br />\n此旅行社的宣傳單張（圖1）上所顯示50078此團價錢為$999，並有4天日子出發，但從（圖2）可見，此公司的網上已沒有此團號的團，已轉為（圖3）的團號<br />\n<br />\n另外$999此價錢並不都是4天日子出發的格價，更不是50078此團號的價格。<br />\n<br />\n另外（圖1）中可見公司叫職員塗鴉字樣，不讓客人觀察得到，因為50078此團的確是沒有購物的，但50088的是有購物點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2t4xyu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2t4xyu.jpg&h=3a25f2fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wifnjdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwifnjdv.jpg&h=3bc2d53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdbYB0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdbYB0b.jpg&h=4479e129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人已sd email海關就商品說明條例作查詢並提出舉報<br />\n我地唔可以比呢間旅行社繼續咁樣呃人，佢地搵到錢就會再贊助tvb，咁亦等同支持tvb<br />\n<br />\n小弟第一次開呢啲po，如有任何問題請多多見諒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b06ed2e62ba2c69e1efed785aa4015a23d4c2059","tid":1367073,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"自己推一推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30915486fbf08269acc81da85dd0d95b2e5718af","tid":1367073,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"得廢老仲玩旅行團<br />\n後生既本身都少幫襯"},{"pid":"0343d9ae1316b58c5489d2946706aaa40e03ee78","tid":1367073,"uid":12816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"都無人報名 封條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e9066c24f57957d9158f0f035e4eaa65018c34","tid":1367073,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30915486fbf08269acc81da85dd0d95b2e5718af","tid":1367073,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"得廢老仲玩旅行團<br />\n後生既本身都少幫襯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"就係因為有銀髮族出黎遊行，所以先要提佢地就算報名都唔好報呢啲陰濕旅行社<br />\n當然我都知報親嘅廢中廢老都唔理香港發生緊乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af8ca19278d07c8e7a3182118bc8132cbfdd1c7","tid":1367073,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0343d9ae1316b58c5489d2946706aaa40e03ee78","tid":1367073,"uid":12816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"都無人報名 封條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"都唔係㗎，每日都有成百幾人報<br />\n所以先想話比果啲仲報團嘅人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}